channel.title: Comments on: Duran Duran collaborate with Timberlake, Timbaland

item.title: By: pathisel
item.dc:creator: pathisel
item.description: the new tracks sound great, the ones that have "leaked" so far are "Nite Runner" "Skin Divers" and "Falling Down", the release date for the titled "Red Carpet Massacure" is Nov. 13th. It SOUNDS VERY PROMISING. See ya later to Andy Taylor, he'll be back in another decade or two to try to catch on to the gravy train.......
item.content:encoded: the new tracks sound great, the ones that have “leaked” so far are “Nite Runner” “Skin Divers” and “Falling Down”, the release date for the titled “Red Carpet Massacure” is Nov. 13th. It SOUNDS VERY PROMISING. See ya later to Andy Taylor, he’ll be back in another decade or two to try to catch on to the gravy train…….
